/06/07/175035_bfe66673969a68e6800d047b631a5130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F175035_bfe66673969a68e6800d047b631a5130.jpg&h=0d84ac1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/175036_d0d138c237bb61695096e9fd934dc46c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F175036_d0d138c237bb61695096e9fd934dc46c.jpg&h=b787f49b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n圖片係pita gyros同炸芝士 兩樣都係2.9 euro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平到仆街</blockquote><br />\nPita gyros原來係野食名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩係入面？"},{"pid":"68b7416051f98d75ffae2a177f576d001cf60b13","tid":274352,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完 無啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能我唔識搵</blockquote><br />\n我都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炸魷魚幾好食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麵包同沙津都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但肉類好多都偏咸同鞋唔太岩口味"},{"pid":"f5f8c415773594b8603b8c5e33408bf24490d1a3","tid":274352,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.fionatree.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Santorini-octopus-fionaTree-1024x768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fionatree.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2FSantorini-octopus-fionaTree-1024x768.jpg&h=cdf12142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八爪魚鬚<br />\n成條過好好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n幅圖上網揾既</span></blockquote><br />\n在哪！</blockquote><br />\n係藍色屋仔果面海旁既露天餐廳